    "description": "Meat-free sausages. Smooth mash. Onion marmalade? Not your regular trio, we know. It's onion marmalade that gives your plant-based gravy a rich tang, bringing this British comfort classic to life. Vibrant green beans and oven-roasted carrots make it full of goodness too!",
